           <strong>Personal Crisis Hotline<br></strong>
          </div> 
          <div class="panel-body">
           <p>If you are experiencing a crisis and need someone to talk to, call the suicide hotline:</p> 
           <p>1-800-273-TALK<br>&nbsp;<br>(1-800-273-8255)<br><br>TTY: 1-800-799-4899</p> 
          </div> 
         </div> <p><a href="mailto:jonessl10@vmi.edu">Lt. Col.&nbsp;Sarah Jones</a><br>Director<br>Center for Cadet Counseling<br>Office of Disabilities Services</p> <p>P: (540) 464-7667<br>F: (540) 464-7025<br>E: <a href="mailto:jonessl10@vmi.edu">jonessl10@vmi.edu</a></p> <p>2nd Floor VMI Health Center<br>Virginia Military Institute<br>Lexington, VA&nbsp; 24450</p></address> 
